All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
Maze
A maze to be traversed by various different robots.
MemoryRobot
MemoryRobot is an implementation of a Robot where it uses a depth-first search to go solve the maze by always going to a unvisited position if possible.
Position
A basic position in a 2d space.
RandomRobot
RandomRobot is an implementation of a Robot where every step is randomized between all possible steps.
RightHandRuleRobot
RightHandRuleRobot is an implementation of a Robot where the robot mimics the classic "right hand on wall" trick to solve a maze.
RobotTest
A simple test for creating a maze and letting RandomRobot solve it.
